<item>
            <title>[PIG-308] Flatten is not being set to true in joins</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-308</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Queries that use the JOIN keyword are returning incorrect results because the flatten values are not being set to true for the foreach that is put after the cogroup.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12400252">PIG-308</key>
