                            <comment id="12614510" author="alangates" created="Thu, 17 Jul 2008 19:54:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue was not flatten being set.  That was done properly.  The issue was that in rewriting the join to the cogroup the parser was incorrectly connecting the resulting foreach to the load instead of the cogroup, and it was incorrectly setting the projects to star instead of two the appropriate columns.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
